romance of the western chamber ( chinese : 西廂記 ; pinyin : xīxiāngjì ) is a 1927 silent chinese film drama directed by hou yao . the film is an adaption of the classic chinese dramatic work romance of the west chamber by wang shifu . originally consisting of ten film reels , only 5 reels have survived . the 2007 usa dvd release by cinema epoch has an additional original musical score composed by toshiyuki hiraoka .